com.radiotelescope.service.s3

Interface IAwsS3UploadService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    S3UploadService

    public IAwsS3UploadService

    Interface used for for uploading files to the AWS Simple Storage Service. Keeping this as an interface allows the application to use test implementations during testing that will not actually contact AWS.
